<html>
  <head>
    <link href="css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/animate.css">
    <style>.wow:first-child {visibility: hidden;}</style>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="login.css">
    <style>.wow:first-child {visibility: hidden;}</style>
  	<title>IdeaTouch</title>
  </head>

  <body>
    <div id="topo">
      <div id="clearance" class="sign-in">
        <div class="hh4"><%= render partial: '/sessions/form' %></div>
      </div>
    </div>

      <div class="box-1">
            <br>
            <h2><img src="/assets/img/160.png" width="100" alt="logotipo" ></h2>
            <div class="tituloFont">IDeaTouch</div>
            <h1>Integrate group dynamics digitally</h1>
            <br>
            <div class="phraseFont">It helps people/companies to collaboratively find solutions best suited to their problems.</div>
            <div class="phraseFont">It lets you define the problem, collect ideas and vote on the best ones.</div>
            <br>
            <div class="hh4"><%= render partial: '/sessions/form2' %></div>
      </div>

      <div class="whatistitle wow fadeInUp" data-wow-duration="0.4s" data-wow-delay="0.4s"><h3>What is IDeaTouch?</h3>
      <div class="imageWhatIs wow fadeInUp" data-wow-duration="0.5s" data-wow-delay="0.5s"></div>
        <div class="boxtext wow fadeInUp" data-wow-duration="0.6s" data-wow-delay="0.6s">
          <p>It is a platform to help people/companies to find solutions best suited to their problems</p>
          <p>It enables the creation, management and implementation of solutions generated collaboratively</p>
          <p>It can be used remotely or in person. Synchronously or asynchronously</p>
          <p>It lets you define the problem, collect ideas, vote on the best ones and the generation of statistics</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="boxhowitworks wow fadeInUp" data-wow-duration="0.4s" data-wow-delay="0.4s">
      <div class="howitworkstitle wow fadeInUp" data-wow-duration="0.5s" data-wow-delay="0.5s"><h3>How it works?</h3></div>

      <div class="stepsBox">
      <div class="step wow fadeInRight" data-wow-duration="0.4s" data-wow-delay="0.4s">
        <h4>1. Avatar and nickname</h4>
        <p>Choose a pre-defined avatar or upload one.</p>
        <p>Then write a nickname.</p>

        <div class="minion wow fadeInUp" data-wow-duration="0.5s" data-wow-delay="0.5s"></div>
        <p>Bill Gates</p>
      </div>

      <div class="step wow fadeInRight" data-wow-duration="0.6s" data-wow-delay="0.6s">
        <h4>2. Create/join Dynamics</h4>
        <p>Create and join dynamics.</p>
        <p>Creating a dynamic, you can invite people to collaborate.</p>

        <div class="dynamicAzul2 wow fadeInUp" data-wow-duration="0.6s" data-wow-delay="0.6s"><div class="hhpp">Dynamic</div></div>
      </div>

      <div class="step wow fadeInRight" data-wow-duration="0.7s" data-wow-delay="0.7s">
        <h4>3. Create Boards into Dynamics</h4>
        <p>Create a Board to put the ideas which are related with it.</p>
        <p>They will be better organized.</p>

        <div class="boardRed2 wow fadeInUp" data-wow-duration="0.5s" data-wow-delay="0.5s"><div class="hhpp">Board</div><a>2</a></div>
      </div>

      <div class="step wow fadeInRight" data-wow-duration="0.8s" data-wow-delay="0.8s">
        <h4>4. Send Notes to solve the challenge</h4>
        <p>Then you can launch ideas.</p>
        <p>You can also pre-select ideas, and vote on the best ones.</p>

        <div class="notaAzulClaro2 wow fadeInUp" data-wow-duration="0.4s" data-wow-delay="0.4s"><div class="hhpp">1</div>write here! </a></div>
      </div>
    </div>
    </div>

<div class="boxadvantagesofplatform wow fadeInUp" data-wow-duration="0.4s" data-wow-delay="0.4s">
      <div class="advantagesofplatformtitle wow fadeInUp" data-wow-duration="0.5s" data-wow-delay="0.5s"><h3>What are the advantages?</h3></div>

      <div class="imageSession wow fadeInUp" data-wow-duration="0.6s" data-wow-delay="0.6s"></div>

      <div class="boxtext wow fadeInUp" data-wow-duration="0.4s" data-wow-delay="0.4s">
        <p>The user can share his ideas remotely or in person</p>
        <p>The user can see ideas from other employees in a more organized way</p>
        <p>The user can pre-select an idea and then vote on the ones he likes more</p>
        <p>IDeaTouch ensures anonymity to users, thus allowing them to feel more comfortable</p>
      </div>
    </div>



    <div class="joinus wow fadeInUp" data-wow-duration="0.5s" data-wow-delay="0.5s">
      <h3>What are you waiting for? Join us!</h3>
      <div class="logoicon wow fadeInUp" data-wow-duration="0.6s" data-wow-delay="0.6s"></div>
      <br>
    </div>

    <h3><div class="hh4"><%= render partial: '/sessions/form2' %></div></h3>

 <!-- javascripts-->
  <script src="js/wow.js"></script>
    <script>var wow = new WOW(
  {
    boxClass:     'wow',      // animated element css class (default is wow)
    animateClass: 'animated', // animation css class (default is animated)
    offset:       0,          // distance to the element when triggering the animation (default is 0)
    mobile:       true,       // trigger animations on mobile devices (default is true)
    live:         true,       // act on asynchronously loaded content (default is true)
    callback:     function(box) {
      // the callback is fired every time an animation is started
      // the argument that is passed in is the DOM node being animated
    }
  }
);
wow.init();
    </script>

  </body>
</html>